{"tid":1559060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"惠譽下調港鐵信貸評級　評級展望為「負面」","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T05:10:46.000Z","uid":20933,"like":961,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":147,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa6bb9914f2d72628ce2ddaf579fdd7bb60256a","tid":1559060,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:09:38.000Z","msg":"評級機構惠譽繼日前下調香港信貸評級後，今晚宣布下調了港鐵（0066）的信貨評級，由「AA+」降至「AA」，評級展望為「負面」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n惠譽解釋，由於下調了香港的主權評級，基於港鐵與香港政府的聯系及策略上的重要性，因此相應下調了港鐵的評級。往後如果香港的主權評級前景有改善，或者港鐵與政府的聯繫減少，才會對港鐵的評級有正面影響。<br />\n<br />\n惠譽在上周五下調了香港的主權評級，同樣由「AA+」降至「AA」，評級展望同樣為「負面」。該行今日解釋，是由於香港在經濟、金融及政治上與內地愈趨融合，因此與內地的評級差距亦要相應收窄。"},{"pid":"5a52e1c9e3138a5a184f55057862150c4b7c134a","tid":1559060,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:09:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568127316436&amp;issue=20190910\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568127316436%26issue%3D20190910&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRetRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=11c68420\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1568127316436%26issue%3D20190910&h=9311adc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1568127316436&amp;issue=20190910</a>"},{"pid":"b568c9470f7f3ced28079b7ebfe67c47c331fff7","tid":1559060,"uid":85425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e269c92b059d441cf8647824a6ef24b42af0f52f","tid":1559060,"uid":170771,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:10:31.000Z","msg":"我願榮光歸香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af39e2b14e4c